{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"論正官","id":"zzq.seg.officer.heading","layer":"editorial","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"論正官","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"chapter_heading"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"官以尅身雖與七煞有別終受彼制何以切忌刑冲破害尊之若是乎","id":"zzq.seg.officer.principle.doctrine","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"官以克身雖與七煞有別終受彼制何以切忌刑衝破害尊之若是乎","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"conceptual_doctrine"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"豈知人生天地必無矯焉自尊之理雖貴極天子亦有天祖臨之正官者分所當尊如在國有君在家有親刑冲破害以下犯上烏乎可乎","id":"zzq.seg.officer.principle.analogy","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"豈知人生天地必無矯焉自尊之理雖貴極天子亦有天祖臨之正官者分所當尊如在國有君在家有親刑衝破害以下犯上烏乎可乎","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"social_analogy"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"以刑冲破害為忌則以生之護之為喜矣","id":"zzq.seg.officer.formation.likes-dislikes","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"以刑衝破害為忌則以生之護之為喜矣","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"formation_doctrine"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"存其喜而去其忌則貴而貴之中又有高低者何也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.formation.evaluation","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"存其喜而去其忌則貴而貴之中又有高低者何也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_evaluation"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"以財印並透者論之兩不相礙","id":"zzq.seg.officer.formation.dual-support","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"以財印並透者論之兩不相礙","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"formation_rule"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"其貴也大","id":"zzq.seg.officer.formation.outcome","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.world.officer.65"],"normalized_search_text":"其貴也大","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_outcome"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"如薛相公命甲申壬申乙巳戊寅壬印戊財以乙隔之水與土不相礙","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.xue.structure","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.57","loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.136","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.65","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"如薛相公命甲申壬申乙巳戊寅壬印戊財以乙隔之水與土不相礙","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example_structure"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"故為大貴","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.xue.outcome","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"故為大貴","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_outcome"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"若壬戌丁未戊申乙卯雜氣正官透干會支","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.lesser-rank.structure","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"若壬戌丁未戊申乙卯雜氣正官透干會支","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example_structure"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"最為貴格","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.lesser-rank.evaluation","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"最為貴格","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_evaluation"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"而壬財丁印二者相合仍以孤官無輔","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.lesser-rank.support-conflict","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"而壬財丁印二者相合仍以孤官無輔","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example_mechanism"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"所以不上七品","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.lesser-rank.outcome","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"所以不上七品","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_outcome"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"若財印不兩用則單用印不若單用財以印能護官亦能減官而財生官也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.single-support","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"若財印不兩用則單用印不若單用財以印能護官亦能減官而財生官也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"comparative_rule"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"若化官為印而透財","id":"zzq.seg.officer.transformation.rule","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"若化官為印而透財","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"transformation_rule"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"則又為秀而大貴之格","id":"zzq.seg.officer.transformation.evaluation","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"則又為秀而大貴之格","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_evaluation"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"如金狀元命乙卯丁亥丁未庚戌此並用財印無傷官而不雜煞所謂去其忌而存其喜者也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.jin","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"如金狀元命乙卯丁亥丁未庚戌此並用財印無傷官而不雜煞所謂去其忌而存其喜者也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"然而遇傷雜煞亦可轉敗為功","id":"zzq.seg.officer.rescue-overview.introduction","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"然而遇傷雜煞亦可轉敗為功","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"rescue_doctrine"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"轉而有情其格愈奇","id":"zzq.seg.officer.rescue-overview.evaluation","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"轉而有情其格愈奇","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_evaluation"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"故遇傷在于佩印混煞貴乎取清","id":"zzq.seg.officer.rescue-overview.doctrine","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"故遇傷在於佩印混煞貴乎取清","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"rescue_rule"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"如宣參國命己卯辛未壬寅辛亥未中己官透干用清支會木局兩辛解之是遇傷而佩印也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.xuan","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"如宣參國命己卯辛未壬寅辛亥未中己官透干用清支會木局兩辛解之是遇傷而佩印也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"李參政命庚寅乙酉甲子戊辰甲用酉官庚金混煞乙以合之合煞留官是雜煞而取清也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.li","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"李參政命庚寅乙酉甲子戊辰甲用酉官庚金混煞乙以合之合煞留官是雜煞而取清也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"至于官格透傷用印者又忌見財以財能去印未能生官而適以護傷故也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.damage","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.58","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"至於官格透傷用印者又忌見財以財能去印未能生官而適以護傷故也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"damage_rule"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"然亦有逢財而反大貴者","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.fan.outcome-introduction","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.59","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"然亦有逢財而反大貴者","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_outcome"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"如范太傅命丁丑壬寅己巳丙寅支具巳丑會金傷官丙丁解之透壬豈非破格却不知丙丁並透用一而足以丁合壬而財去以丙制傷而官清","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.fan.mechanism","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.59","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"如范太傅命丁丑壬寅己巳丙寅支具巳丑會金傷官丙丁解之透壬豈非破格卻不知丙丁並透用一而足以丁合壬而財去以丙制傷而官清","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"classical_example_mechanism"}
{"chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","diplomatic_text":"無情而愈有情此正造化之妙變幻無窮","id":"zzq.seg.officer.example.fan.evaluation","layer":"example","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.59","loc.qin.officer.137","loc.world.officer.66"],"normalized_search_text":"無情而愈有情此正造化之妙變幻無窮","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"historical_evaluation"}
