{"audit_id":"OU0","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"論正官取運","id":"zzq.seg.officer.period-heading","layer":"editorial","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou1"],"normalized_search_text":"論正官取運","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"chapter_heading"}
{"audit_id":"OU1","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"取運之道一八字則有一八字之論其理甚精其法甚活只可大略言之變化在人不可泥也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou1","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou1"],"normalized_search_text":"取運之道一八字則有一八字之論其理甚精其法甚活只可大略言之變化在人不可泥也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
{"audit_id":"OU2","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"如正官取運卽以正官所就之格分而配之正官而用財卽身稍輕則取助身官稍輕則取助官若官露而不可逢合不可襍煞不可重官與地支刑冲不問所就何局皆不利也正官用財運喜印綬身旺之地切忌食傷若身旺而財輕官弱卽仍取財官運可也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou2","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou1"],"normalized_search_text":"如正官取運即以正官所就之格分而配之正官而用財即身稍輕則取助身官稍輕則取助官若官露而不可逢合不可雜殺不可重官與地支刑衝不問所就何局皆不利也正官用財運喜印綬身旺之地切忌食傷若身旺而財輕官弱即仍取財官運可也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
{"audit_id":"OU3","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"正官佩印運喜財鄉傷食反吉若官重身輕而佩印則身旺為宜不必財運也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou3","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou1","loc.gc.officer.audit-ou2"],"normalized_search_text":"正官佩印運喜財鄉傷食反吉若官重身輕而佩印則身旺為宜不必財運也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
{"audit_id":"OU4","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"正官帶傷食而用印制運喜官旺印旺之鄉財運切忌傷食反為不礙若印綬疊出財運亦無害矣","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou4","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou2"],"normalized_search_text":"正官帶傷食而用印制運喜官旺印旺之鄉財運切忌傷食反為不礙若印綬疊出財運亦無害矣","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
{"audit_id":"OU5","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"正官而帶煞其命中用比合煞則財運可行傷食可行身旺印綬亦可行只不可復露七煞若命用傷官合煞則傷食與財俱可行而不宜逢印矣","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou5","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou2"],"normalized_search_text":"正官而帶殺其命中用比合殺則財運可行傷食可行身旺印綬亦可行只不可復露七殺若命用傷官合殺則傷食與財俱可行而不宜逢印矣","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
{"audit_id":"OU6","chapter_id":"zzq.pattern.direct-officer","coverage_status":"full_paragraph","diplomatic_text":"此皆大略言之其八字各有議論運中每遇一字各有講究隨時取用不可言形凡格皆然不獨正官也","id":"zzq.seg.officer.audit-ou6","layer":"shen_core","locator_ids":["loc.gc.officer.audit-ou2"],"normalized_search_text":"此皆大略言之其八字各有議論運中每遇一字各有講究隨時取用不可言形凡格皆然不獨正官也","review_state":"scan_verified","text_type":"period_boundary_attestation"}
